The existing surface of the Quarry Moor car park has significantly deteriorated, requiring urgent resurfacing to ensure safety, durability, and compliance with relevant standards. 
Key issues include: 
•	A deep depression at the car park entrance;
•	A low point at the entrance;
•	Potholes exceeding 40mm in depth.

