River Lugg IDB ("IDB") intends to commission a hydraulic model of its open channel watercourse network in order to achieve the following:
•	Gain a more comprehensive understanding of fluvial flood risk from the IDB network;
•	Provide an evidence-based decision-making tool to be used to support future capital works funding applications for structures and for undertaking works on the system and/or maintaining the systems.
